  "bio": {
    "short": "Dave Knowles is a South African composer, multi-instrumentalist, and live loop artist whose performances weave guitar, sax, violin, flute, and voice into immersive soundscapes. With a career spanning indie rock, folk, theatre, children's television, and experimental electronica, Dave brings a genre-blending performance full of energy, improvisation, and heart.",
    "acoustic": "Dave Knowles delivers dynamic acoustic performances, blending percussive guitar grooves with soulful melodies and lyrical storytelling. A seasoned folk artist, his live shows are intimate, powerful, and unforgettable.",
    "full": []
  },
